然坚守一中政策，不支持台湾的「国家身份」，不支持台湾加入以主权国家为资格的国际组织。与此同时北京实现统一的意志越来越顽强，强调「任何人都不要低估中国人民捍卫国家主权和领土完整的坚强决心、坚定意志、强大能力」，「在这个现实之下，妄想台湾独立完全不切实际」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-2dabaf91eb62040b41f49c742b6a6740_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "677 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/470580147"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ir+6WmcLpq5AzEAMaCDY2ODUyOTAwIJqBlIcGMA44zgJABHIJNDcwNTgwMTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1625641306.7349038", "card_id": "Q_470431274", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 AI 杀入斗地主领域，快手 DouZero 击败 344 个 AI 排名第一？未来人类斗地主能斗过 AI 吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "快手团队开发的斗地主 AI 命名为 DouZero，意思是像 AlphaZero 一样从零开始训练，不需要加入任何人类知识。 只用 4 个 GPU，短短几天的训练时间，就在 Botzone 排行榜上的 344 个斗地主 AI 中排名第一。AI 杀入斗地主领域，快手开发 DouZero 对标 AlphaZero，干掉 344 个 AI 获第一 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-98ac926f10adddaf2e3377ec59890c61.jpg?source=2044ae36"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "630 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/470431274"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ir+6WmcLpq5AzEAMaCDY2ODE5Nzc0IKeDkIcGMBk40AZABXIJNDcwNDMxMjc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1625641306.7354755", "card_id": "Q_23026542", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 129}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么编程语言有这么多种类？为什么不统一成一种语言呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "统一了不更好吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e8d0610d0785b17dd634e8c050fadd4_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "498 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/23026542"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Ir+6WmcLpq5AzEAMaBzEzOTE0ODYgt